data.description: Welcome to the epitome of luxurious living in the prestigious Silver Oaks community! This meticulously maintained gem offers an unparalleled combination of elegance, convenience, and natural beauty.    Nestled on a sprawling yard that gracefully merges with the lush green fairways of the adjacent golf course, this home is a true haven for golf enthusiasts and nature lovers alike. Silver Oaks, an established and picturesque community, sits just moments away, providing you with easy access to all the shops, restaurants, and entertainment you could ever desire.    Step inside this 1,528 sqft masterpiece, and you'll be greeted by an open concept layout that exudes sophistication. No detail has been overlooked, and no expense has been spared when it comes to the top-notch materials used in crafting this residence. High ceilings add an air of grandeur, infusing every room with an abundance of natural light.    But the true magic unfolds as you step onto the expansive screened lanai. This outdoor oasis is perfect for entertaining or simply unwinding in style. It boasts a fire pit, hot tub, grill, and a dining set with four chairs and a table – all included. Imagine evenings spent under the starlit sky, creating cherished memories in your very own private retreat.    This isn't just a house; it's a lifestyle upgrade. Your opportunity to own a piece of Silver Oaks luxury has arrived. Don't miss out on the chance to make this impeccable property yours today!
